Applications directory for Simulations using Geant4

G4ExSimulator:
Contains example simulation application with its documentation.

G4RockSimulator:
Application intended to simulate a block of rock with (optionally) scintillator detectors in a given position.

G4BarSimulator:
Application used for the simulation of the response to traversing muons through a plastic cintillator bar, 
with WLS fiber coupled to a photo-detector device (SiPM / PMT).


